  "texts": [
    "She said, \"It would be super helpful if I could use all the images on the moodboard as input.",
    "The data from all these images will be so much richer than one single sentence.",
    "\"3.1.4 Fine-tuning prompts to control the outcome: More than half of the participants commented with comparative phrases such as \"too many plants\" or \"less colorful\" regarding the generated images.",
    "Most prompt tuning based on this feedback failed as it is difficult to turn these comparative phrases into effective AI prompts.",
    "P4 tried to add \"less green plants\" directly in the prompt, however, still generated an image with a similar amount of green plants as before."
  ]
